.jumbotron
  %h1 Wonderpedia
  %p A community-sourced collaboration platform.
  %p
    = link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path, class: 'btn btn-primary'
    or
    = link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-primary'
.row
  .col-md-6
    %h3 This is the place where you can post a wiki for a hobby or work-related project. 
    %h3 Wonderpedia allow you to create your own wikis and share them publicly or privately with other collaborators.
  .col-md-6
    %h4 For $15, you can get a lifetime premium membership!
    %br
    %p Sign up and then upgrade your membership.
    %br
    %p Why become premium?
    %ul
      %li You can create private wiki and collaborate with other
      %li users to make your wiki more awesome!
